ivileges extend to increased trust and more freedom.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 179, 231);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 180, 229);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 181, 227);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 181, 225);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(134, 182, 223);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 183, 222);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 184, 220);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 185, 218);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 185, 216);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 186, 214);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 187, 212);\">︵</span></p><p>↪ <span style=\"color: rgb(78, 217, 233);\"><strong>Gunko's notes</strong></span></p><blockquote><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This bot is dedicated to the one Taff fan (Vesa) in the Critter Den. I am NOT proud of his older bots, I recently re-did their bios to be token efficient, so I decided to just write a short alt as a make up for mermay since I did have one planned for it! Mermay-ke up.</span></p></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 179, 231);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 180, 229);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 181, 227);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 181, 225);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(134, 182, 223);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(152, 183, 222);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 184, 220);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(189, 185, 218);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(207, 185, 216);\">︵</span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 186, 214);\">‿</span><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 187, 212);\">︵</span></p><p>You can find me in the server I share with <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/7501de02-9f05-46e9-8412-458953aeaadd_profile-of-mirjuno\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 81, 182);\"><strong>Mirjuno </strong></span></a>and <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"